r\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time, the opening ceremony will not take place in a stadium.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, dozens of boats will carry thousands of athletes and performers on a 6km floating parade on the Seine on July 26.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3032716681060232e-21, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6km floating parade\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Explosive detection canine handler, Anais Roman, and her dog Nikky, checked one of the boats set be part of the ceremony, docked near the Pont de Bercy on Sunday morning.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\", \"score\": 0.9504612022612818, \"rank\": 0.052026134869896455, \"text\": \"Roman\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\"}, {\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_de_Bercy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\"