 {\"ngram\": \"his reward\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Generally, everything's going well,\\\" said chief superintendent of the areas around Paris, Zeljko Ilic.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.009543306958348e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"chief superintendent\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"the areas\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"Zeljko Ilic\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A police officer and a sniffer dog inspect a boat on the river Seine that will take part in the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A police officer\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"a sniffer dog\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"a boat\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Gonzalo Fuentes/Reuters He added that the \\\"colossal task\\\" of inspecting parade boats, private vessels and floating establishments open to the public like restaurants and bars to secure the banks of the Seine required international police to \\\"lend a hand\\\".\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3032716681060232e-21, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": 