, \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"the river inspections\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Departing from the Austerlitz bridge, the parade will sail by Notre-Dame de Paris Cathedral and arrive near the Eiffel Tower, after passing under bridges and gateways, including the Pont des Arts and Pont Neuf, and near many of the French capital's landmarks.\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"score\": 0.9999909125494014, \"rank\": 9.087533276440604e-06, \"text\": \"Austerlitz\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_d'Austerlitz\"}, {\"begin\": 1859, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont des Arts\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_des_Arts\"}, {\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Neuf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.955277965728296e-41, \"text\": \"Pont Neuf\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Neuf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Neuf\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7997528307428695, \"rank\": 0.21487061580724776, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the parade\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre-Dame de Paris Cathedral\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"gateways\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 45,000 police will be dispatched to ensure the ceremony's security, including special intervention forces.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some 45,000 police\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's security\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"special intervention forces\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snipers will be deployed on the top of buildings along the route.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Snipers\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An anti-drone system will be in place.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An anti-drone system\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With wars in Gaza and Ukraine, and security concerns at home, France already has its security alert at its highest level.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2169, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.6013299323628423, \"rank\": 0.6629805805117023, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 2178, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999928632723829, \"rank\": 5.536014365625776e-06, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996528280780672, \"rank\": 0.000178914611802721, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wars\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"security concerns\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"its security alert\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"its highest level\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, with more than 300,000 spectators expected to watch, it is also a major security headache.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 300,000 spectators\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"a major security headache\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a six km route, so it's a huge perimeter to monitor.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a six km route\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge perimeter\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why we need that many (security) people,\\\" Konstantinidis, the Games' head of planning and coordination, told reporters.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that many (security) people\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"Konstantinidis\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' head\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"planning\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"coordination\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our security plans are very dynamic.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our security plans\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They always take into consideration the latest events and try to adapt,\\\" he said during a tour of the Games' security headquarters, Last Saturday's assassination attempt against former U.S. president Trump at an election rally in Pennsylvania has not changed the security plans for the Games, Konstantinidis said.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9998887200970334, \"rank\": 0.00011091364808169095, \"text\": \"president Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.9999836915137333, \"rank\": 1.2216287320125118e-05, \"text\": \"Pennsylvania\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"consideration\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest events\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"a tour\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' security headquarters\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"Last Saturday's assassination attempt\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"an election rally\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"the security plans\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"Konstantinidis\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have very close collaboration with the U.S. security services and its secret service.\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very close collaboration\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. security services\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"its secret service\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are sharing also any information we have,\\\" Konstantinidis said.\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any information\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"Konstantinidis\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are very confident that we are on the same page but we have not had to change any of our plans as a result of that very unfortunate incident.\\\"\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same page\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"our plans\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"that very unfortunate incident\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 100 people will be working around the clock at the Games' security headquarters in Saint-Denis, just outside Paris, he said.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3319, \"end\": 3330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9998551133077611, \"rank\": 0.00014487096027644925, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 3345, \"end\": 3350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.009543306958348e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 100 people\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' security headquarters\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials have added there were no specific terror threats to the July 26 ceremony, with Zeljko saying that security was \\\"largely assured\\\" for visitors to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3371}, {\"ngram\": \"no specific terror threats\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"the July 26 ceremony\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3444}, {\"ngram\": \"Zeljko\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3457}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Come with a free spirit and enjoy the games,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a free spirit\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toStoryboard\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"CGTN\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3661}, {\"ngram\": \"every Friday SITEMAP EXPLORE\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"OUR APP\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3755}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"010-85061466 SITEMAP\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"OUR APP\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\